EN: In this classroom, please take your seats at your designated spot.
ZH: 请大家就座等候上菜。
EN: Please take your seats and wait for the food to be served.
ZH: 会议将在5分钟后开始，请就座等候。
EN: The meeting will start in 5 minutes, please take your seats and wait.
ZH: 请勿在就座后再次起立。
EN: Please do not stand up again after taking your seats.
ZH: 我们可以在这里就座吗？
EN: Can we take our seats here?
